metadata.name: SNEAKERBOX NFT #1
metadata.description:
We are a Web2 brand established in 2009 and a fully on-chain collection of NFTs living on the Ethereum Blockchain.

Our brand mission is to create opportunity through sneakers. We exist simply to help humans, and give back through charitable work, scholarships, access, and experience. Our IRL partnerships and network is what allows us to do so.

If you mint a Sneakerbox NFT, not only are you getting really cool art, rewards and utility, but you are helping people in need.
